% Krishna Salad Dressing
% Krishna Lunch at UF; Colin Chan

# Acquire

*   1 cup sliced almonds
*   1/2 heaping cup nutritional yeast (maybe more)
*   1.1 cup safflower oil
*   1.1 cup water
*   2 tbsp Bragg liquid aminos
*   1/6 tsp asafoetida powder (strong stuff)

# Prepare

1.  Roughly powder the almonds in a blender. 10 to 15 quick pulses should do
    it.
2.  Add the remaining ingredients, and blend for 30 seconds.
3.  Refrigerate.
